text: Monique Adamczak and Olivia Rogowska were the defending champions, having won the event in 2013, however both players chose not to participate. The Australian-duo Jessica Moore and Abbie Myers won the title, defeating Thai- sisters Varatchaya and Varunya Wongteanchai, 3–6, 6–1, [10–6]. == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Bendigo Women's International 2 - Doubles
